Very proud and thankful for getting the chance to be a part in the transformation of PSA Antwerp's Europa Terminal. This is the first phase of the yard conversion from manually operated straddle carriers to highly automated, remote controlled endloaded ASCs. We are looking forward to a great project and more to come for following phases.
